<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٢٠٧٧ - <span class="c2">(٥)</span> <span class="c4">[ضعيف]</span> ورُويَ عنْ عَلّيٍ رضيَ الله عنه قال:<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>خَرجَ رسولُ الله - صلى الله عليه وسلم -<span class="c5"> فإذا نِسْوَةٌ جُلوسٌ قال:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c1">"ما يُجْلِسُكُنَّ؟ "</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">قلْنَ:</span> نَنْتَظِرُ الجَنازَةَ.<span class="c5"> قال:</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c1">"هل تُغَسِّلْنَ؟ "</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">قلْنَ:</span> لا.<span class="c5"> قال:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c1">"هَلْ تَحْمِلْنَ؟ "</span>.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">قُلْنَ:</span> لا.<span class="c5"> قال:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c1">"تُدْلينَ فيمَنْ يُدْلي؟ "</span>.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
